value: Breeds along the Arctic coast (and islands immediately north) of North America from Point Barrow, Alaska, to southeastern Baffin Island and Southampton Island. Migrates chiefly through the Mississippi Valley (but abundant in Labrador in late summer) and winters in southern South America, chiefly east of the Andes, from Paraguay to the Straits of Magel- lan; Falkland Islands.
